&lt;p>The GT IEEE Robotech Hackathon might not be the biggest event, but it was my first real dive into an intensive hackathon-style build. Despite freezing rain and wind, everyone showed up. Our four-member team, TachyAstroach, kicked off the mission.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>About Me</title><link>https://career.purticra.icu/about/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hlyu68@gatech.edu (Hongyi Lyu)</author><guid>https://career.purticra.icu/about/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="relative group">Hi, I&amp;rsquo;m Hongyi
